by javiereguiluz at 2019-10-03T11:37:06Z

Naming things is hard ðŸ˜“  So, after talking with Nicolas, I've renamed this again following his suggestion (I think that the new name is equally self-explanatory, but even easier to understand and avoids problems like the division by zero):

```php
minSecondsBetweenRedraws(float $seconds)
maxSecondsBetweenRedraws(float $seconds)
```
